quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  66,1,"Eehey ma nelaa…óo ko saabii ha…óa harmina ko Alla dagnan ma fii dakmitaade e kor…óo ma Maariya, ko sabu ha…óa faala heen welnaade suddii…ìe ma nde …ìe kirnoo nde, Alla na yaafa ma na yurmo ma."
  66,2,"Alla sariyanii on dagtinde goondoote mon e kaffaara si on he…ìii ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude wolla njan…óon e woondoore he,ko Alla woni balla mon,ko kanko woni ganndu…óo fiyakuui mon e ko mo∆¥∆¥i e mon; √ëee√±a e sariya makko e hoddira makko."
  66,3,"Siftor nde Annabi-yo o his-heerirani hafsa kabaaru, ina e hembo wonde O …ìadataako cuddii…óo makko Maariya, hafsa haalani aa*isa kabaaru o, Alla anndini annabi makko saaktaade sirru o, O feli hafsa O haalani mbo yogo e yeewtere he o fanki ko heddii ko, hafsa wi*i Mbo hombo haalan ma o kibaaru? O maaki habrii kam Gannda kala huunde kumpatii…óo kala ko wirni."
  66,4,"Ina wa…ó…óii e mon nde tuubaton sabu …ìer…óe mon naayiima e ko Nelaa…óo Alla a√±i …óum woni wo…ó…óitaade kor…óo makko e harminde mbo e hoore makko, si on ndooniima e waylaade e dow makko, pellet Alla ko ballo makko, ko noon kadi jibriil e uul…ìe labaa…ìe ko walladii …ìe mbo e Malayka en caggal ballugol Alla ko…ìe walloo…ìe mbo e dow loroowo Mbo."
  66,5,"Yaama de joomiiko cenii…óo O si annabi makko seerii…ìe O wostanoo mbo suddii…ìe …ìur…ìe mon mo∆¥∆¥ude, …óowtii…ìe jamirooje Makko, goon…óin…ìe Alla e nelaa…óo makko, …óoftii…ìe Alla, tuuboo…ìe bakkatuuji mum en, rewoo…ìe jom mum en, hooroo…ìe, seemed…ìe e boomi …ói naatdaaka tawa, kono tan O seeraani …ìe."
  66,6,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe Alla ngolliri ko O sarayini ko e mum en, mba…óane ko*e mon e koreeji heeda e yiite nge docate mannge ko yim…ìe e kaa…ìe, ina e dow nge yiite Malayka en sattuu…ìe e naatoo…ìe e henge, …ìe ngoopatah yamiroore Alla si O yamirii…ìe, ho…ìe mba…óa ko …ìe njamira ko, ko aldah e leelde."
  66,7,"Na wiyanee heefer…ìe √±ande darnga: eehey mon heefer…ìe, wotee ngantinee hannde ko ngonno…óon e yeddude e woopde, Alla gantinantaa on, njo…ìete…óon hannde tan ko ko ngollatna…óo e aduna ummaade e keefeeru e fennude nulaa…ìe."